title: AIR International Special - F-35 Lightning II
description:
AIR International Special - F-35 Lightning II

46 Pages | HQ PDF | English | 10 MB 


AIR International has been on the road, visiting production and flight test facilities around the world to compile this 46-page special.  Its intention is to explain how the aircraft and its major systems work, and how the F-35 handles in flight based on accounts from the test pilots who fly it. The F-35 is undoubtedly unlike any fighter aircraft built to date, and is bristling with complex and revolutionary systems.
